Revision history for Perl extension Text::Embed.

0.03  Thu Jun 16 12:19:00 2005

    - improved POD
    - tidied source
    - modified #define syntax to accomodate single-line constants

0.02  Thu Mar 31 16:53:11 2005

    - made POD clearer
    - improved regular expressions in utility functions
    - added block-noindent/block-indent options

0.01  Mon Mar 28 13:27:45 2005
	- original version; created by h2xs 1.23 with options
		-AXO -b 5.6.0 -n Text::Embed

    - added comment stripping
    - added utility functions
    - added arbitrary callbacks
    - added call by reference semantics to callbacks

